<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/32004521">中二病太强是怎样一种体验？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="5001171" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">这里是每天晚上刷牙会挥动牙刷低吼一句：“海贼库里，唔哩哇拿路！”的中二病患者→_→</div>


